<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="take-it-easy-take-things-easy">take it easy / take things easy</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>放松；不急；不紧张：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He should learn to take things easy.
他应该学会放松。</p><footer>2015 天津</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Take it easy, Peter. I'll help you out.
别着急，彼得，我来帮你解决。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Try not to work yourself too hard. Take it easy.
别太辛苦了，轻松点</p><footer>2012 全国</footer></div></div>